Package steganography.audio.overlays

Interface AudioOverlay

All Known Implementing Classes:
MockMP3Overlay, MP3SequenceOverlay, MP3ShuffleOverlay
public interface AudioOverlay
The implementing classes should be able to returns data bytes of an audio file independent from their order in the file.
